Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.21,0:01:05.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(448,616)}爱哭男孩
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.05,0:01:09.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.05,0:01:09.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.38,0:01:11.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天可是个特别的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:11.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is a very special day today
Dialogue: 1,0:01:11.21,0:01:14.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我们要播出爱哭男孩的全新单曲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:14.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,because we've got the new single from boys who cry
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.40,0:01:16.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是主角
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.40,0:01:16.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all about you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.52,0:01:18.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:18.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all about you, girl
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.05,0:01:21.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,庆祝你十六岁生日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:21.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On your 16th birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.75,0:01:23.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们目光向你看齐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.75,0:01:23.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll pay attention to you, girl
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家对你言听计从
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone has to do just what you say
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.30,0:01:30.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚全场灯光聚焦于你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:30.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll get your very own spotlight tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.99,0:01:33.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你就是主角
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:33.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause it's all about you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.15,0:01:35.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:35.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's all about Pearl
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:36.28,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(376,278)}珍珍
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.63,0:01:37.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是寿星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.63,0:01:37.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the birthday girl
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.65,0:01:40.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我就是主角
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.65,0:01:40.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's all about me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.33,0:01:41.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:41.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.34,0:01:43.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,庆祝我十六岁生日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.34,0:01:43.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On my 16th birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.46,0:01:47.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要音乐跟衣服  还有亮晶晶的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.46,0:01:47.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want music and clothes and shiny things
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.75,0:01:50.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快快掌声鼓励
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:50.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So give it up right away
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.63,0:01:53.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全世界的大众
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.63,0:01:53.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody in the whole wide world
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.02,0:01:55.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,目光向我看齐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:55.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they have to pay attention to me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.32,0:01:57.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主角就是我  我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:57.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all about me, me
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.58,0:01:58.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再猜猜是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:01:58.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And guess who
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:00.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.25,0:02:06.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:06.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Neptune's trousers
Dialogue: 1,0:02:06.65,0:02:08.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早安  老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:08.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Morning, daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:08.83,0:02:12.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你确定不要睡一楼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:10.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you wouldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:12.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,prefer a room on the ground floor?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.52,0:02:13.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:13.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:13.35,0:02:17.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是兴奋嘛  因为明天可是特别日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:17.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just excited because tomorrow's a very special day
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.20,0:02:18.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:18.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.85,0:02:22.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说  确实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.85,0:02:22.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, it is
Dialogue: 1,0:02:22.10,0:02:24.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很特别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:24.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very special
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.00,0:02:26.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,的确非常非常特别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:26.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Very, very special indeed
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不知道明天是什么日子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:29.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You have no idea what day tomorrow is, do you?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.33,0:02:30.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:30.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,None at all
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.22,0:02:33.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天是我十六岁生日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:33.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's my 16th birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.98,0:02:34.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:34.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew that
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么会以为我不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How could you think I wouldn't know that?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.55,0:02:38.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,长到几岁  十二吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:38.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you going to be, 12?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.92,0:02:41.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要十六岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.92,0:02:41.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be 16
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.50,0:02:44.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我一生唯一最重要的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:44.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's only the most important birthday in my entire life
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.95,0:02:47.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要是没有棒得不得了的派对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:47.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I don't have a completely awesome party
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.37,0:02:49.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会在整个高中生涯都抬不起头来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:49.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my whole high school reputation will collapse
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.97,0:02:50.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能被迫辍学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:50.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have to drop out
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.96,0:02:52.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没法上大学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:52.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't go off to college
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.57,0:02:53.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出不了家门一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:02:53.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never leave home
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我后半辈子都得让你来养
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll have to support me for the rest of my life
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那种事情绝对不能发生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we don't want that to happen
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.86,0:03:04.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就保证今年给我办个真正的派对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:04.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then promise me you'll give me a real party this year
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.10,0:03:05.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许小气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:05.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And don't be cheap
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:07.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1014,456)}高中
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.47,0:03:09.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  姐妹们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:09.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, girls
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.92,0:03:10.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:10.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.71,0:03:11.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:11.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you guys coming
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.53,0:03:14.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,明天来参加我的生日炫派对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:14.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to my totally coral birthday party tomorrow?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.20,0:03:15.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好吧  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:15.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.55,0:03:18.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这次派对会不会跟去年一样炫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:18.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is this going to be as totally coral as last year
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.89,0:03:22.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那时你爸还发回形针当派对礼物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:22.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when your dad passed out paper clips as party favors?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.91,0:03:26.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记得那回咱都只能共用一个气球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.91,0:03:26.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember the time we all had to share one balloon?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:03:27.50,0:03:28.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,记得骑小马不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:28.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Remember the pony ride?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.47,0:03:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等不及要看他今年怎么个搞砸法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.47,0:03:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to see how he ruins this year
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:37.82,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(644,344)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:39.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全体做好防撞姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody, brace for impact
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.98,0:03:48.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快说你给我生日派对准备了炫东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:46.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Tell me you've got something totally coral
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.41,0:03:48.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,planned for my birthday party
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你别急嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, now, don't snap your mizzenmast
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.30,0:03:52.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:52.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everything is all set
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.95,0:03:55.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都已经买好派对礼物了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:55.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I've already got the party favors
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡泡包装膜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:57.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble wrap
Dialogue: 1,0:03:57.91,0:04:00.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今年一定会特别劲爆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:04:00.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This year's gonna be a blast
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.45,0:04:03.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸  你搞砸了我先前所有生日派对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:03.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy, you ruined all my birthday parties
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好别给我把这次也搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:05.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you better not ruin this one
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,答应我  不要小气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, promise me you won't be cheap
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我答应
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.35,0:04:09.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promise
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.01,0:04:11.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我列了张清单
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:11.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because I made a list
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:15.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(972,458)}正在驶出裤头村
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.87,0:04:19.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,清单上的东西都得在派对上配齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:19.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, I want everything on this list at my party
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.45,0:04:21.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:21.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.07,0:04:24.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟我朋友去逛商场了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:24.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll be at the mall with my friends
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.02,0:04:26.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:26.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:27.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.44,0:04:28.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我布置派对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:28.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,While I plan the party
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就由你负责去买珍珍的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I want you to buy Pearl's present
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.56,0:04:31.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:31.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this, Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.27,0:04:34.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我的信用卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:34.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me credit card
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以拿它当钱用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:35.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You use it instead of money
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.49,0:04:38.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用这个塑料片就可以买东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:38.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can buy stuff with just this piece of plastic?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:38.52,0:04:39.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用不着钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:39.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need money?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.88,0:04:40.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:40.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了  什么都配不上我的小珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now remember, nothing's too good for me little Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.85,0:04:46.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我虽然本来想什么都不给她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:46.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanted to give her nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是她不应该什么都不配
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But she's too good for that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快跟踪她  看她喜欢什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:51.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now follow her around and see what she likes
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是去干包打听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.12,0:04:53.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, do some detective work
Dialogue: 1,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,包打听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Detective work
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.47,0:04:56.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要卧底了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:56.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going undercover
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.48,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(754,552)}裤头村商场
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那时候玛西跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So that's when Marcie told me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:00.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(682,404)}商场
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.13,0:05:04.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,茱莉说安吉拉她确实喜欢布拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:04.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that Julie said that Angela did like Brad
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.77,0:05:07.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安吉拉喜欢布拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.77,0:05:07.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Angela likes Brad
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:08.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.69,0:05:12.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是我见过世上最棒的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.69,0:05:10.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the greatest thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have seen in the whole world
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:18.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(306,200)}收银
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.30,0:05:18.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要用这片塑料买那块塑料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:16.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to buy that piece of plastic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with this piece of plastic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(250,836)}鲤事达\N尤金蟹先生
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.52,0:05:21.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.52,0:05:21.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹这个字怎么写
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:23.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do you spell "Krabs"?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面肯定有个虫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure it has a "b" in it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.20,0:05:26.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:26.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Close enough
Dialogue: 1,0:05:28.72,0:05:29.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去吧  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:29.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.57,0:05:30.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:30.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.10,0:05:34.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我永远不懂高级金融是如何运作的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:34.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll never understand the workings of high finance
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.05,0:05:38.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是我全世界见过最棒的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:36.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the greatest thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:38.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've ever seen in the whole world
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.85,0:05:40.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,闪光唇彩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:40.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Glitter gloss
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.81,0:05:41.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:41.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.81,0:05:43.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我买错礼物了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:43.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bought the wrong present
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.32,0:05:45.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  一定要来看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:45.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, you have got to see this
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.57,0:05:46.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来了  朱迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:46.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coming, Judy
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.03,0:05:55.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个一看就是最棒的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:55.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, this is obviously the greatest present ever
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:55.54,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1082,288)}美妆
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.84,0:06:00.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是全世界最棒的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:06:00.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the greatest thing in the whole world
Dialogue: 1,0:06:02.86,0:06:05.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,横幅挂好了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:05.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The banner's up, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她出生那天我就买了那横幅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:07.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've had that since the day she was born
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特地趁着特价买的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got it on sale
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:11.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(596,276)}喜得贵子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:11.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(684,280)}女\N×
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.42,0:06:11.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她一定会喜欢的  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:11.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll love it, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:18.10,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(430,234)}宠物
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.36,0:06:18.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这匹小海马最可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:18.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This sea pony is the cutest thing ever
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想不想回家当我的小马驹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you want to come home and be my pony?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.79,0:06:28.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.79,0:06:28.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, come here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:28.83,0:06:30.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个可炫了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:30.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is so coral
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:35.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(750,882)}狗鱼                   小海马
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:37.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是比利鱼金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's Billy fishkin
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.04,0:06:40.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  比利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:40.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Billy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他好俊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't he dreamy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.46,0:06:52.35,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(624,136)}促销
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四号收银台需要确认价格
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Price check on four
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.91,0:06:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍的塑像做好了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I finished Pearl's portrait, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.21,0:06:57.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好一个旷世巨作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.21,0:06:57.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a true masterpiece
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早知道就雇佣先前那个冰雕师傅了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should have hired that ice sculptor
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么冰雕师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:03.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ice sculptor?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,冰雕连傻子都会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.40,0:07:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any fool can sculpt in ice
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有真正的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It takes true genius
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.19,0:07:10.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能做到把四百磅蟹黄堡生肉饼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:10.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to transform 400 pounds of raw krabby patties
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.50,0:07:13.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,塑造成此般的巨作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:13.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,into a work of such majesty
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.16,0:07:14.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:14.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.36,0:07:17.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,装饰算是办妥了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:17.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, we've got the decor covered
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.02,0:07:18.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,娱乐又是怎么个事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:18.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, how about entertainment?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:18.32,0:07:19.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.32,0:07:19.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me see here
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.30,0:07:23.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍想要个叫做爱哭男孩的男团
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.30,0:07:23.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl wants some boy band called boys who cry
Dialogue: 1,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱哭男孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boys who cry?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.58,0:07:25.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们可是我最爱的男团
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:25.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're my favorite band
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.12,0:07:29.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,出场费可是要一百万啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:29.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They charge a million dollars just to show up
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要他们假唱得花大钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you want them to lip-sync, it'll run into real money
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是真爱粉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a real fan, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.65,0:07:33.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:33.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.78,0:07:35.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们的歌我都懂一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:35.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know all their songs
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们的歌你都懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All their songs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:54.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(670,196)}墨镜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:08:00.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(824,136)}鞋               贵帽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:08:00.41,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1262,874)}垃圾
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.84,0:08:10.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爸给我这个当生日礼物一定会很酷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:10.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be cool if my dad got me this for my birthday?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.72,0:08:12.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实  前提是他得先酷再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:12.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sure would be, if he was cool
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.96,0:08:13.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可惜他不酷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:13.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Which he's not
Dialogue: 1,0:08:15.02,0:08:18.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  他可能又要给我送一盒订书钉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:18.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he probably got me another box of staples
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对就快要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for the party to start
Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.05,0:08:24.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我回来了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.05,0:08:24.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm back, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  干什么耗这么久
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:26.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what took you so long?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:26.27,0:08:27.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍的礼物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:27.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And where's Pearl's present?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.86,0:08:30.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,送快递的车马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:30.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The delivery truck will be here momentarily
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她来了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here she comes, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.96,0:08:34.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全体就位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:34.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody get in position
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.28,0:08:39.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:39.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(702,440)}喜得贵子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(790,444)}女\N×
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喜得贵子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:41.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"It's a boy"?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.92,0:08:44.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:44.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:52.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(958,208)}爆米花
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.62,0:08:52.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爆米花都馊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:52.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stale popcorn
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.88,0:08:56.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,味道像刷锅水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:56.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It tastes like dishwater
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.15,0:08:58.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来就是刷锅水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:58.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is dishwater
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那玩意是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:03.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that supposed to be me?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:04.99,0:09:07.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用蟹黄堡肉饼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:07.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's made out of krabby patties
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.07,0:09:08.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:08.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gross
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁要吃蛋糕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who wants cake?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.52,0:09:13.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蛋糕看着挺好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:13.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the cake does look good
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.85,0:09:18.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这蛋糕用纸板做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:18.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's made out of cardboard
Dialogue: 1,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加了糖霜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:19.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And frosting
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.30,0:09:20.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:20.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.97,0:09:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你派对连土16次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,16 lame parties in a row
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想必是破纪录了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:25.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Must be a new record
Dialogue: 1,0:09:25.42,0:09:26.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们还是走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:26.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.99,0:09:27.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:27.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:09:27.70,0:09:28.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:28.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't leave
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.97,0:09:31.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我爸请了爱哭男孩来演出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.97,0:09:31.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My dad got boys who cry to play
Dialogue: 1,0:09:31.52,0:09:33.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你请到了爱哭男孩对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:33.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You did get boys who cry, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.98,0:09:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比那更好呢  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even better, sweetie
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.73,0:09:36.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:36.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hit it
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小姐们好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, ladies
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.34,0:09:43.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每当我泪水流个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:43.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When my tear ducts give issue
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.22,0:09:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能用随便什么纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't use just any tissue
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须要四层
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need four-ply
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.12,0:09:50.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四层
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:50.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Four-ply
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四层
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:51.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Four-ply
Dialogue: 1,0:09:51.08,0:09:52.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才哭得动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.08,0:09:52.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When I cry
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就不是爱哭男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:56.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That is not boys who cry
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,烂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boo
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.12,0:09:59.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太劣质了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:09:59.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a rip-off
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.83,0:10:00.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好个垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:00.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This stinks
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.70,0:10:04.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸  你怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:04.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy, how could you?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.27,0:10:08.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都给你清单了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:08.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gave you a list
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.65,0:10:13.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珍珍  回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:13.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl, come back
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是全都让你给搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.40,0:10:20.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ruined everything
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.32,0:10:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干什么都小气  就连对我都小气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You couldn't stop being cheap, even for me
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.69,0:10:29.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会想办法补偿你的  珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:29.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll make it up to you somehow, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.20,0:10:31.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:31.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Back it up
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.60,0:10:32.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒到这来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:32.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right there
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.58,0:10:34.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,倒下来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:34.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let 'er go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你给我买了艘船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You bought me a boat?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.07,0:10:44.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:44.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.99,0:10:45.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:45.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.08,0:10:46.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:46.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.25,0:10:53.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸  不知道一切还能再好到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:53.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy, I don't know how it could get better than this
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just watch
Dialogue: 1,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hit it, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.62,0:11:02.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是女主角
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:02.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all about you, girl
Dialogue: 1,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,庆祝你十六岁生日
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:05.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,On your 16th birthday
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.76,0:11:08.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们目光向你看齐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:08.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll pay attention to you, girl
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家对你言听计从
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everyone has to do just what you say
Dialogue: 1,0:11:11.50,0:11:14.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今晚全场灯光聚焦于你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:14.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll get your very own spotlight tonight
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为你就是主角
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'Cause it's all about you
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.12,0:11:19.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也就是珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:19.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's all about Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就是寿星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're the birthday girl
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.08,0:11:20.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:20.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些花了我多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How much is all this costing me?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.65,0:11:23.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是收据
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:23.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's the receipt
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.70,0:11:26.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我非得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:26.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ought to--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.23,0:11:28.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.23,0:11:28.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Daddy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.05,0:11:31.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你给了我想要的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:31.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got me everything I wanted
Dialogue: 1,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么都配不上我的小珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:36.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing's too good for me daughter
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.44,0:11:39.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真是个好爸爸  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:39.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a good dad, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:11:40.15,0:11:42.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别得寸进尺  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.15,0:11:42.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't push your luck, boy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:45.45,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}空手道岛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.04\pos(232,456)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:47.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.04\pos(487.502,730)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:51.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:49.24,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.04\pos(399.315,562.667)}客串
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:51.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.63\pos(382.547,425.334)}技术总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:51.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.63\pos(512.728,679.334)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:52.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz30.04\pos(421.346,538.667)}制片指导
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:52.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.666,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.92,0:11:58.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.17,0:12:00.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好来做一年一次的背壳打蜡没
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:12:00.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ready for your yearly shell waxing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:01.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1134.301,443.476)}壳蜡
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.35,0:12:09.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:09.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at that shine
Dialogue: 1,0:12:09.97,0:12:11.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来进壳里看一看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:11.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let's check under the hood
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.48,0:12:14.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:14.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Geez, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方脏得跟蜗牛圈似的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this place is a real snail-sty
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.19,0:12:17.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一直没清
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:17.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Still?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.98,0:12:18.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跨年夜就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.98,0:12:18.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,From New Year's Eve?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.65,0:12:21.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:21.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.19,0:12:23.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一直都在到处找这个呢  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:23.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been looking everywhere for this, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.82,0:12:26.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我最爱的新奇搞怪T恤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:26.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My favorite novelty t-shirt
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.45,0:12:28.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:28.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Someone's here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.49,0:12:33.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给海绵宝宝的特别快递
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:33.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Special delivery for SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别快递
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Special delivery?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.62,0:12:36.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:36.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just for me?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.17,0:12:38.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你觉得我很
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.17,0:12:38.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think I'm
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.83,0:12:39.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,特别吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.83,0:12:39.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,special?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.09,0:12:43.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:43.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 1,0:12:43.17,0:12:46.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每次给你送快递都非得遭这种罪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:44.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,do we have to go through this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:46.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,every time I give you your mail?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.72,0:12:48.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天会是什么呢  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:48.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What could it be today, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.85,0:12:50.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个录像带
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:50.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A videotape?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.89,0:12:52.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是大赢家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:52.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"You're a winner --
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.56,0:12:54.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:54.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants"
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空手道岛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.86,0:13:01.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karate Island
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:01.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(709.944,885.934)}空手道岛
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.40,0:13:05.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个充满自然与美景的宁静异域之地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:03.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A serene and exotic location
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:05.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where nature and beauty abound
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.40,0:13:07.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,几百般武艺在此碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:07.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and hundreds of fighting styles collide
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且永不停息  紧张刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in a wave of non-stop, pulsating
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.61,0:13:11.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无拘无束地行动着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:11.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no-hold barred action
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:11.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(722.01,735.096)}行动
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.03,0:13:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,几个世纪以来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For centuries
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.87,0:13:14.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世界顶尖空手道大师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.87,0:13:14.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the world's top karate artists
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来到这片热土
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,have journeyed to this land
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加冕成为空手道之王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:18.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to be crowned King of Karate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.12,0:13:18.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(703.911,767.274)}空手道
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.04,0:13:21.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空手道之王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:21.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,King of Karate?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn
Dialogue: 1,0:13:22.79,0:13:24.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:24.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.59,0:13:25.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你赢得了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:25.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've won
Dialogue: 1,0:13:25.17,0:13:28.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,前往空手道岛的全额免费旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:28.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,an all-expense paid trip to Karate Island
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.13,0:13:29.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(713.967,883.924)}空手道岛
Dialogue: 1,0:13:29.43,0:13:33.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你将在此加冕为今年的空手道之王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:33.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where you'll be crowned this year's King of Karate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:33.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(715.977,186.047)}空手道之王
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听到了吗  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that, Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要被加冕为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:38.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be crowned
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.31,0:13:42.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空手道之王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.31,0:13:42.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,King of Karate
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.45,0:13:53.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:53.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.08,0:13:54.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:54.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.99,0:13:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你听说了没
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:56.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have you heard the news?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要受邀去空手道岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:58.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've been invited to Karate Island
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加冕为空手道之王
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:59.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to be crowned the king of karate
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.96,0:14:00.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空手道岛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:00.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karate Island?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:00.92,0:14:02.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我没听说过空手道岛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:02.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of Karate Island
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.63,0:14:03.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.63,0:14:03.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.17,0:14:04.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空手道大师都会过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:04.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all the big karate experts go there
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.88,0:14:08.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我空手道强得都能甩你好几条街了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:08.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, my karate is better than yours by a country mile
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.05,0:14:09.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,岛那边从来没邀请过我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:09.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I've never been invited
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.47,0:14:11.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,也许你空手道确实挺强
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.47,0:14:11.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe your karate was the best
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.55,0:14:13.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过现在那边认了个新的第一了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:13.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but now they've recognized a new number one
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.68,0:14:15.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉有哪里不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:15.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's something rotten in the Alamo
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.97,0:14:17.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最好还是跟你一起过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:17.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd better tag along with you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看里面靠不靠谱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.31,0:14:18.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and see if it's on the up-and-up
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.56,0:14:19.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.56,0:14:19.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:14:19.64,0:14:22.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以随我前来目睹我的加冕时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:22.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can come with me to witness my crowning moment
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.32,0:14:27.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.32,0:14:27.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are we there yet?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.03,0:14:27.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:27.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.86,0:14:28.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:28.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it over there
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.32,0:14:31.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么会知道那是空手道岛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:31.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What make you think that's Karate Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:33.66,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(961.34,540.014)}欢迎来到空手道岛
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道  刚好猜中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know, lucky guess?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.75,0:14:48.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好啊  空手道之王大驾光临
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:48.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello there, the King of Karate has arrived
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.71,0:14:51.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临我的岛  海绵宝宝桑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:51.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to my island, SpongeBob-san
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.80,0:14:53.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:53.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.18,0:14:55.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是乌冬大师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:55.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am Master Udon
Dialogue: 1,0:14:55.39,0:14:56.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  乌冬大师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.39,0:14:56.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Howdy, Master Udon
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.72,0:14:57.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:57.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy Cheeks
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自己也会一点空手道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do a little karate myself
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.68,0:15:01.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪珊迪珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.68,0:15:01.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, Sandy, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.64,0:15:04.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乌冬大师对你这种空手道菜鸟没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.64,0:15:04.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Udon isn't interested in a karate novice like you
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他只有加冕的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He only has time for royalty
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:08.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, brother
Dialogue: 1,0:15:08.94,0:15:13.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请你向我展示几招  海绵宝宝大师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:10.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, show me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:13.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,some of your moves, Master SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听见没  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:14.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You hear that, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.61,0:15:16.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他叫我  大师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:16.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He called me "master"
Dialogue: 1,0:15:16.53,0:15:18.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们最好的打手都放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.53,0:15:18.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring on your best fighters
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.24,0:15:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尽量温和对待他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll try to go easy on 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.87,0:15:24.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你空手道还不够强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:24.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, your karate's not good enough
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打不过那几位硬茬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:25.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to handle those sidewinders
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,边看边学  小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch and learn, sister
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.01,0:15:38.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空手道之王就这么强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:38.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's how the King of Karate does it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.39,0:15:39.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下一个是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.39,0:15:39.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's next?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.10,0:15:42.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点十分不对劲的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:42.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something smells like rancid rodeo around here
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.27,0:15:45.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:45.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excellent
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.60,0:15:48.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不愧是空手道之王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.60,0:15:48.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Truly, you are King of Karate
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.69,0:15:49.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,独一无二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:49.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The one and only
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.77,0:15:53.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要做好准备为你举行加冕典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:53.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We must make ready for your coronation
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.24,0:15:56.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好成为空手道之王了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:56.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to be King of Karate
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空手道之王桑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,King of Karate-san
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.66,0:16:01.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你现在是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:01.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it is time for you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.79,0:16:05.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要坐上属于你的宝座了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:05.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to take your rightful place on your throne
Dialogue: 1,0:16:05.71,0:16:07.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的宝座
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:07.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My throne
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.21,0:16:12.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  乌冬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.21,0:16:12.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, Udon
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.38,0:16:13.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我盯着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.38,0:16:13.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on to you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.72,0:16:16.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这地方感觉有诈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:16.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This place is as crooked as a dizzy sidewinder
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.34,0:16:17.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.34,0:16:17.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.39,0:16:18.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在空手道之王旁边就座
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.39,0:16:18.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,take your place next to the king
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,分享我的巅峰时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and share in my crowning achievement
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我呼吸空气的朋友带个位子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring a seat for my air-breathing friend
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.81,0:16:32.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你都滑头起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.81,0:16:32.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, y'all are getting a bit wily
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是不是察觉到了一丝妒忌呢  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do I detect a note of jealousy, Sandy?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:34.78,0:16:37.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能用空手道把你打得落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:37.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Heck, I could karate you into a country fiddle
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.66,0:16:39.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就算一只爪子绑背后也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:39.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with one paw tied behind my back
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.53,0:16:42.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是加冕为空手道之王的是谁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.53,0:16:42.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But who's being crowned King of Karate?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.49,0:16:43.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:43.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not you
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.79,0:16:45.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不陪你闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.79,0:16:45.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm getting off this crazy train
Dialogue: 1,0:16:47.29,0:16:49.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大师  别理她了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:49.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Master, don't worry about her
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.75,0:16:53.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她就快错过这千载难逢的好机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She is missing out on the opportunity of a lifetime
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.30,0:16:57.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,加冕仪式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:57.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let the coronation begin
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪就快错过大好时机了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy's going to miss out, big time
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.69,0:17:13.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,该死的海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.69,0:17:13.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That dang SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.19,0:17:14.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他以为他谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:14.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who does he think he is?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.36,0:17:17.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那黄色自私鬼的格斗知识都是我教的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.36,0:17:16.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I taught that yellow egomaniac
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:17.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,everything he knows about fighting
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.61,0:17:18.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且还只是一点皮毛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:18.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and that ain't much
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.74,0:17:21.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:21.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.24,0:17:22.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.24,0:17:22.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob's in trouble
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.70,0:17:26.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝可是空手道之王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:26.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob is the "King of Karate"
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,根本就不需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:27.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He doesn't need me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他自己就能解决
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He can handle this himself
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.08,0:17:30.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:30.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.83,0:17:32.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我自己没法解决
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:32.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't handle this myself
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坚持住  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:34.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold on, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.17,0:17:35.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:35.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.92,0:17:37.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:37.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.80,0:17:39.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她绝对没法救到你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:39.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She will never reach you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.47,0:17:44.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她必须先通过  四层恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:44.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She must first pass through the "Four Floors of Fear"
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.69,0:17:51.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要想过去  必须先打败我搔痒哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:51.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You cannot pass unless you defeat me, The Tickler
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.81,0:17:53.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有我的铁指禅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:53.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and my iron-finger style
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.28,0:17:58.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:17:58.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.78,0:18:04.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备迎接你的一生之痒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.78,0:18:04.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prepare for the tickling of your life
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.24,0:18:06.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尝尝这些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:06.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Taste these
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.58,0:18:08.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:08.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.25,0:18:10.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果酱馅甜甜圈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.25,0:18:10.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jelly-filled donuts?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道那是我的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you know they were my weakness?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果酱馅的吸引力无人能敌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:14.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one can resist jelly-filled
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.38,0:18:23.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黏在那别动  等会再回来给你上糖浆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:23.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sticky around, I'll be back with the glazed
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.55,0:18:25.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要湿巾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:25.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could use a wet napkin
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.39,0:18:27.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好了  下一个是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:27.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, who's next?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.68,0:18:28.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:28.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Halt
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.85,0:18:33.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人可以通过我大嘴女这关
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:33.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one advances past me, Lipp Cervas
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.73,0:18:37.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有我的伸缩嘴唇冲刺术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.73,0:18:37.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and my power-flexi dynamo-lip thruster style
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.61,0:18:43.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跳舞啊  小松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:43.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dance, squirrel, dance
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进阶吹风机招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:48.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Advanced hair-dryer style
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.41,0:18:51.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你用那玩意想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:51.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you expect to do with that?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.67,0:18:57.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:57.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.09,0:18:59.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嘴唇不能干
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:59.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not chapped lips
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:02.13,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(701.9,793.42)}唇膏
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.05,0:19:06.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你少废话了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:06.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's enough lip out of you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:06.60,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(752,920)}嘴 唇
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.40,0:19:18.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还没人能抵达肮脏菲尔的老巢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:18.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one has ever made it to the lair of Filthy Phil
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.86,0:19:22.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除了我没人能过关
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:22.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one passes except me
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.03,0:19:28.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来感受我可怕体臭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:28.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, feel the steam of my horrible body odor
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.50,0:19:36.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Phil
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.25,0:19:38.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的恶臭可透不过我的新鲜空气罩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:38.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your foul stench can't permeate my fresh-air dome
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.13,0:19:40.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新鲜空气罩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.13,0:19:40.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fresh-air dome?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.05,0:19:46.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也太臭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:46.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Man, I really do stink
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.60,0:19:54.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这位松鼠还挺强的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:54.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are one impressive squirrel
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.52,0:19:56.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,连衣服都换了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:56.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You even made a costume change
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.31,0:19:57.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放了海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:57.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Release SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.81,0:19:59.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:19:59.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Never
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.65,0:20:06.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要是想走  得先
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:06.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He is forbidden to leave, until
Dialogue: 1,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,签了这份合同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he signs this contract
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:08.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(931.173,407.275)}合同
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.78,0:20:09.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你在说什么鬼话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:09.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.83,0:20:10.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,房地产
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.83,0:20:10.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Real estate
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.99,0:20:12.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:12.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean this whole thing
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.20,0:20:14.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是骗我们买房地产设的套
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:14.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,was a scam to get us to buy real estate?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.04,0:20:15.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:15.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是真有空手道岛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If there was a real Karate Island
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早就是有钱人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd be a millionaire
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.67,0:20:20.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是说我不是空手道之王吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.67,0:20:20.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You mean I'm not King of Karate?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.96,0:20:21.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:21.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.67,0:20:24.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你可以当公寓之王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.67,0:20:24.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you could be King of Condos
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.88,0:20:26.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来  解释给你听
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:26.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, let me explain
Dialogue: 1,0:20:26.30,0:20:28.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,道理很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.30,0:20:28.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's really quite simple
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.05,0:20:32.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,如果在公寓岛投资分时度假公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.05,0:20:32.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See, if you invest in a time share here on Condo Island
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.39,0:20:36.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你资产就会增长十倍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:36.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can see your equity increase ten-fold
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.48,0:20:39.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你和你的黄色朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:39.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you and your yellow friend
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.56,0:20:42.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该愿意投资分时度假公寓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.56,0:20:42.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,would like to set up a timeshare plan?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.23,0:20:43.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万别投资  珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:43.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.16,0:20:58.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会中你的分时度假公寓圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:58.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I won't give in to your timeshare vacation scam
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就中我的拳头
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:00.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then give into my fists
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.85,0:21:57.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下你泡汤了吧  乌冬面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.85,0:21:57.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're in the soup now, Udon
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.27,0:22:02.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,珊迪  对不起我刚在岛上特别欠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.27,0:22:02.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sandy, I'm sorry I acted like a jerk back there
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.81,0:22:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你解救我脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for saving me from
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.02,0:22:06.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,买公寓骗局
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.02,0:22:06.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,buying a condo
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.61,0:22:08.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是的  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:08.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aw, shucks, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.11,0:22:09.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友就该互挺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.11,0:22:09.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's what friends are for
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.20,0:22:11.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过我还有个问题想问
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.20,0:22:11.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I still have one question, though
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.66,0:22:13.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是不是说我再也不是空手道之王了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:13.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does this mean I'm not King of Karate anymore?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.87,0:22:16.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在我看来你就是  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.87,0:22:16.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are in my book, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.66,0:22:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在我看来你就是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.66,0:22:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You are in my book
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.50,0:22:20.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在我来跟你讲解房地产
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:20.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now let me tell you about real estate
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.37,0:22:22.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,其关键在于选址
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.37,0:22:22.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's all about location
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.54,0:22:25.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.54,0:22:25.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm here
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.96,0:22:29.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,竖笛之王大驾光临
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:29.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The King of Clarinets has arrived
